(508, 1, '2019-11-27 10:19:25', '2019-11-27 10:19:25', 'As an other assessment for this module, I have also study&nbsp;more in details a subject of the creative industry in order to write a complete technical report around it.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nYou can find my <strong>Technical Report</strong> dealing about the<strong> Impact of social, casual and mobile game in the evolving games industry</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://vincent-berthet.net/en/project/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/CA2_B00313298.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">right there</a>', 'Technical Report : Impact of social, casual and mobile games in the evolving games', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '489-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-11-27 10:19:25', '2019-11-27 10:19:25', '', 489, 'http://uwsblog.yo.fr/UWS_Blog/2019/11/27/489-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
