(322, 1, '2016-09-27 18:42:50', '2016-09-27 16:42:50', '<img class=\"size-full wp-image-319 aligncenter\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/mmm.jpg\" alt=\"mmm\" width=\"275\" height=\"183\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHey, my name is Vincent, I am a 20 years old french student. I am currently studying Game Development in the University of the West of Scotland (UWS), and I wish you the welcome on my blog !\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #993366; text-decoration: underline;\">About me\r\n</span></span></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-320 alignleft\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_20160924_161106-2.jpg\" alt=\"img_20160924_161106-2\" width=\"504\" height=\"283\" />\r\n\r\nFor 8 years, computing and video games have taken an important part on my free time. First of all, I have started as a self-educated and I did many projects to discover deeper the computing field.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThat\'s why, I decided to continue my studies in a first time in Electrical Engineering &amp; Industrial Computing during 2 years, in order to discover fields like automations, electronic, embeded computing which were fields that interested myself.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFinaly, I decided to forward in the computing. Instead of chose directly a french engineering school, I have prefered to take this year in a foreign country, in order to improve my english which is a very important skill in this field and also in the profesional world.\r\n\r\nMoreover, I believe that this experience to discover an other culture, way of work, lifestyle, and also one of the interesting specifities of computing (Game Development) is a great opportunity\r\nfor me. Furthermore, I am sure about that this experience will help in my project of study after this year.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #993366; text-decoration: underline;\">About the blog</span></span></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis blog has been designed to cover\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFeel free to add me on your social account !\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-27 18:42:50', '2016-09-27 16:42:50', '', 264, 'http://127.0.0.1/blog/2016/09/27/264-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
